						               													<description>A beaver card game where players compete against each other simultaneously and try to cut down the opponent's trees!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Beaver Brawl requires players to develop alliances in the early game and play in a smart way to avoid the infamous Beaverona card(which would eliminate the player from the game).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After the Beaverona is drawn, the game becomes a pure strategy card game where attack and defend actions need to be performed at the right time not to overexpose the player.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Every player starts with 4 cards in their hands and plays a combination of them every turn to defend their tree or attack someone's tree.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;They draw from the deck the same amount of cards they played.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;When a player draws the Beaverona or loses all its trees, it is eliminated from the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The last player standing wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
